divs: Sighting DetailsTook a photo from my Nokia 6131 phone, we were on vacations, later when downloaded to my computer saw this strange bright light on the top right corner. At the time the photo was taken I did not notice anything in the sky, the location is in an open park called San Martin near Mendoza Capital, in Argentina.
